question.en:
Consider this code snippet:

const stream = fs.createReadStream('file.txt');
stream.on('data', chunk => {
  console.log('chunk:', chunk.length);
});
stream.pause();
stream.on('data', chunk => {
  console.log('paused chunk:', chunk.length);
});
stream.resume();

What will be logged to console?

